{"tid":682702,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"李光洙終闖大禍！節目言語攻擊AOA惠晶 網民聯署青瓦台望討公道","createTime":"2018-05-29T05:42:13.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-01T17:59:30.000Z","uid":63113,"like":5,"dislike":23,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"e451735655cc5726281796f99374ff6d5e9c3855","tid":682702,"uid":63113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T05:42:13.000Z","msg":"南韓近期對女權或其他社會議題十分敏感，甚至嚴重到有人會去青瓦台的請願處請願死刑，李洪基和秀智都曾有過這樣的經驗，而這次又驚見搞笑藝人兼演員的李光洙被請願死刑，全因他在《Runnin Man》中的發言。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/29/133849_fc2930afe7cc7127c16e3cc9f9bd1567.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F29%2F133849_fc2930afe7cc7127c16e3cc9f9bd1567.png&h=fc2a7657&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n最新一集《Running Man》27日播出，邀請到AOA雪炫和惠晶、宇宙少女多榮、MOMOLAND珠伊、WINNER旻浩和昇潤一同參與，到了中間爭取吃飯權力競賽時，昇潤和梁世燦組別和李光洙、惠晶組交換隊員時，殭屍的人數瞬間增加，這也讓人更確信了李光洙和惠晶就是殭屍。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/29/134114_0890de6efe03281da1fe32760d04864b.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F29%2F134114_0890de6efe03281da1fe32760d04864b.png&h=a463428b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n李光洙因為知道自己是一般人，那麼曾經的搭檔惠晶就是殭屍帶原者，當知道這項事實時，他冷笑了一聲對著對方說：「妳是花蛇（꽃뱀）啊。」不過字幕是寫著「騙子（사기꾼）」，部分激進網友認為節目組也認為這句話是不妥當的，氣得上青瓦台網站申請「藝人李光洙死刑請願」，而目前該請願頁面已被刪除，觀眾們也紛紛出面力挺雖然發言有些不當，但並沒有那麼嚴重，「什麼都求死刑，這社會病了」、「綜藝就只是綜藝」、「製作組改字幕也是知道花蛇發言的不當性吧，當初就該剪掉」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/29/134008_efc10524f6cf98928783ca27085d3678.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F29%2F134008_efc10524f6cf98928783ca27085d3678.png&h=9d9f8bba&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n事實上，花蛇（꽃뱀）在韓文中意旨女生靠著華麗的外表接近男性，一點一點慢慢地將男生所擁有的金錢啃食乾淨，或是要對方送名牌包、金銀配飾等貴重物品，男生的錢包就像這樣像被蛇緊緊纏繞一樣，最後空無一物，南韓新聞版面上也常有「花蛇女詐欺」等消息。"},{"pid":"a7dc267664960eff5dea09565ff7164b283e92a5","tid":682702,"uid":53672,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T05:45:32.000Z","msg":"平行世界?南韓女權抬頭?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24849bbeffe826b29e27b7cbf782a5ceb41cc7aa","tid":682702,"uid":38407,"like":2,"dislike":13,"score":-11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T05:47:29.000Z","msg":"抵死la咁樣話我惠晶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e088a36aba364f4035f1c8b63ee965903de469ae","tid":682702,"uid":833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T05:47:53.000Z","msg":"on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce0356b2cbcaec88c6e0e80bba175bdb66e6edb0","tid":682702,"uid":151309,"like":30,"dislike":2,"score":28,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T05:48:21.000Z","msg":"搞下笑都要死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95ef7012bdea215712af063397de1506a0e822d9","tid":682702,"uid":58335,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"a7dc267664960eff5dea09565ff7164b283e92a5","tid":682702,"uid":53672,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T05:45:32.000Z","msg":"平行世界?南韓女權抬頭?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T05:49:32.000Z","msg":"而家南韓女權不嬲都好勁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n南韓兩性都有超極端<br />\n極端女權可以因為個BB係仔走去落左佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7cff5860adfeb55021f1728eff0826d5701ae2f2","tid":682702,"uid":815,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T05:51:29.000Z","msg":"女權真係惡過狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d02dfdb389d957f72144e63f0e95a4a4f85e721